28:52.047 --> 28:54.881
so, it'll be faster
to take the subway.

28:54.964 --> 28:58.005
-Are you sure?
-Yeah. I'm sure.

28:58.798 --> 29:00.339
But thank you.

29:02.964 --> 29:06.297
Oh, hey. It's all right.

29:12.714 --> 29:14.547
Thank you.

29:14.631 --> 29:16.339
For your kindness.

29:26.005 --> 29:27.339
(door closes)

29:32.964 --> 29:34.756
Diane:
Do I hear 80? 80,000?

29:34.839 --> 29:38.089
Gentleman in the front.
90? 90,000.

29:38.172 --> 29:39.422
If we reach 100,000,

29:39.506 --> 29:42.089
