to a child in need.

29:42.172 --> 29:44.547
(crowd laughing)

29:45.130 --> 29:46.089
So what was all that?

29:46.172 --> 29:48.422
What's going on with you
and the nudist?

29:48.506 --> 29:50.547
(exhales) She was upset,

29:50.631 --> 29:53.464
and she just, um,

29:53.547 --> 29:57.297
